u}= \left( egin{array}{cc} 0 & m_D\ m_D^{m T} & M_R\ \end{array}ight)\!,\label{tnumass}\end{equation}$$ where $m_D$ and $M_R$ are given in Eqs. (10) and (11), respectively. The Lagrangian part describing the neutrino mass term is $- rac{1}{2} \overline{
