In the limit $m_{a,b}\rightarrow 0$ with $t_{\beta}=1$ and $t_{\varphi,i}=\frac{m^2_{n_i}}{m^2_{\varphi}}$, the contributions from the charged Higgs bosons $C^{\varphi}_{L,R}$ have the following forms:
